comments.content: I want to say heavily customised [Rubens](http://web.archive.org/web/20080429225046/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/woodentypefonts/rubens/) - but that was probably only the inspiration for this freeware-ish looking font.

If you dig this, you might also like [Metalista](http://web.archive.org/web/20080429225046/http:/www.suitcasetype.com/index.php?lmut=en&part=fonts&font=24) by [Tomáš Brousil](http://web.archive.org/web/20080429225046/http:/typophile.com/wiki/Tom%2525C3%2525A1%2525C5%2525A1%252BBrousil).
